{"tid":1488205,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"機場唔知幾時再停只會加快資金流出","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T14:55:20.000Z","uid":261171,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6095dfcc3ef121e8b9e856276e8c4379af56e6","tid":1488205,"uid":261171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:30:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190819/bkn-20190819175837640-0819_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190819%2Fbkn-20190819175837640-0819_00842_001.html&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NABVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=23bf1c66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190819/bkn-20190819175837640-0819_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n●實體黃金也外逃 <br />\n在這場修例風波中，黃金以另一種方式體驗避險資產的特性，據報，連香港實體黃金也加速逃離。 <br />\n<br />\n為客戶購買，儲存和運輸貴金屬的J. Rotbart＆Co表示，一些客戶擔心內地在香港進行干預，或機場另一次關閉，將使他們的黃金難以搬走，因黃金是在商業航班上運送的。 <br />\n<br />\n該公司觀察到，最近來自香港及中國大陸的新客戶，更傾向將黃金儲存在新加坡，而非香港，兩者比例由之前的50：30，轉變成目前的75：10。"},{"pid":"53f58f8f95d1cd778067eea9811330be97b0d6d2","tid":1488205,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:32:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c12c87c3fa1d4f129a0386698dfe3fe5574d134","tid":1488205,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffe94afcd3634deb